{"title":"vest","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"vengeance-wolf","title":"VENGEANCE WOLF","description":"\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM.\r\n100% French Terry Cotton.\r\nBeads work at the armhole area.\r\nGender- Neutral.\r\nBoxy-Fit.\r\nCombed\r\nBio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCrafted from heavyweight 240 GSM cotton, this oversized sleeveless vest brings raw street attitude with uncompromising quality. The front features a fierce wild wolf snarling under the bold gothic VENGEANCE typography — a symbol of power, rebellion, and untamed spirit. Detailed with beadwork along the armholes, this piece delivers a rugged edge that elevates the silhouette. Iconic biohazard and medic insignias sit beneath the artwork, cementing its post-apocalyptic streetwear vibe.\r\n\r\nThe back carries the VENGEANCE wordmark again with the signature DRIP STUDIOS insignia, marking it as a drop forged in fury.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the vest inside out with like colors.\r\nUse cold water to preserve the fabric’s quality.\r\nTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the fabric’s integrity.\r\nStore the vest in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eVest with 240 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.\r\nOversized fit for comfortable and versatile wear by both men and women.\r\nUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\r\nSoft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/p\u003e\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46853860622490,"sku":"vest(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":46853860655258,"sku":"vest(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":46853860688026,"sku":"vest(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46853860720794,"sku":"vest(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46853860753562,"sku":"vest(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46853860786330,"sku":"vest(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/IMG_7840_11zon.webp?v=1765727363"},{"product_id":"sinner-society-vest","title":"SINNER SOCIETY VEST","description":"\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM.\r\n100% French Terry Cotton.\r\nGender- Neutral.\r\nBoxy-Fit.\r\nCombed\r\nBio-washed\r\n\"Beads work at the arm hole area\"\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Sinner Society Vest is a bold expression of streetwear culture, crafted from premium 260 GSM fabric for superior durability and an oversized fit. The front features a striking DripCult graphic intertwined with a heart, symbolizing passion and defiance. Elevating its design, premium matte-finish metal beads outline the armhole area, adding a unique touch of raw luxury and attitude. On the back, “Sinner Society” is boldly printed alongside the exclusive Drip Signature Number 09′, marking its authenticity. Designed for those who challenge the norm, this vest is a statement of rebellion, confidence, and individuality.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the vest inside out with like colors.\r\nUse cold water to preserve the fabric’s quality.\r\nTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the fabric’s integrity.\r\nStore the vest in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eVest with 260 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.\r\nOversized fit for comfortable and versatile wear by both men and women.\r\nUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\r\nSoft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/p\u003e\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"M","offer_id":46853862064282,"sku":"vest","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":46853862097050,"sku":"vest","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46853862129818,"sku":"vest","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46853862162586,"sku":"vest","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"S","offer_id":46853862195354,"sku":"vest","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46853862228122,"sku":"vest","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DD99_11zon.webp?v=1765727310"},{"product_id":"the-vision-vest-ltd-ed","title":"THE VISION VEST - Ltd. Ed.","description":"\n\u003cp\u003e\"Beads work at the arm hole area\"\r\n240 GSM.\r\n100% French Terry Cotton.\r\nGender- Neutral.\r\nBoxy-Fit.\r\nCombed\r\nBio-washed\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eUnleash your vision with this heavyweight 240 GSM vest, built for the bold. The front features a striking “DRIP STUDIOS” print, paired with classic streetwear art and an embossed logo for a textured, standout finish. On the back, a powerful message—“CREATOR OF MY OWN REALITY”—sets the tone for self-expression and independence. Designed with a relaxed fit and premium cotton, this vest delivers all-day comfort with undeniable presence. Whether you’re on the grind or making a statement, this piece speaks loud. Streetwear isn’t just fashion—it’s a mindset. Own yours with DRIP STUDIOS.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the t-shirt inside out with like colors.\r\n